# Textarea — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/textarea.css`

## CSS Classes

### Structure
- `.acko-textarea` — flex column, gap var(--space-2)
- `.acko-textarea-label` — label-lg typography, color-text-default
- `.acko-textarea-el` — the `<textarea>` element

### Resize (via `.acko-textarea-resize-{vertical|horizontal|both|none}`)
Uses native CSS `resize` property.

### States (on `.acko-textarea-el`)
- Focus: `border-color: var(--color-primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--color-primary)`
- Error: `border-color: var(--color-error)`
- Success: `border-color: var(--color-success)`
- Disabled: `background: var(--color-surface-raised); border-color: var(--color-border-subtle); cursor: not-allowed; color: var(--color-text-disabled)`

### Footer
- `.acko-textarea-footer` — flex justify-between
- `.acko-textarea-helper-text` / `.acko-textarea-error-text` — caption font
- `.acko-textarea-count` — caption font, color-text-muted
- `.acko-textarea-required` — red asterisk
